probably cleared up by now.

00:05:15.370 --> 00:05:18.340
The heel of my shoe is rammed
up against the face of someone

00:05:18.340 --> 00:05:21.630
that ended up below me and the
weight of the ones on top ends

00:05:21.630 --> 00:05:24.590
up ramming it in even further.

00:05:24.590 --> 00:05:28.980
