face and both we trembled of joy

00:08:49.750 --> 00:08:51.910
when I asked you to come with me.

00:08:51.910 --> 00:08:54.400
Because there was no
more loneliness.

00:08:54.400 --> 00:08:57.410
I saw you weep, lifting
your burned eyelids to me.

00:08:57.410 --> 00:09:00.360 position:56%
