those moors we loved.

00:09:06.470 --> 00:09:10.770 position:56%
That's how we were among the
overgrown pastures and we became one

00:09:10.770 --> 00:09:12.420
and promised ourselves forever.

00:09:12.420 --> 00:09:14.890
But you broke your promise.

00:09:14.890 --> 00:09:16.530
You forgot about when I found you

00:09:16.530 --> 00:09:18.520
